{"tid":443453,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"（iOS/an)有無人會玩 勇者鬥惡龍 卡牌版","createTime":"2017-10-21T14:52:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-13T04:55:48.000Z","uid":152533,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"89add8f74f6d445c67d05f001321de491b919e35","tid":443453,"uid":152533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T14:52:46.000Z","msg":"由日本 Square Enix 公司預定於 2017 年 11 月上旬在 iOS／Android 等手機平台上推出營運，目前預約註冊活動也正在官網火熱展開中的這款數位卡牌對戰新作《勇者鬥惡龍：競爭者們》（Dragon Quest Rivals／ドラゴンクエストライバルズ，中文名暫稱），如今官方正式宣佈，本作將預定於 2017 年 11 月 2 日起正式在日本 App Store／Google Play 推出上架！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n等玩<br />\ngameplay<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/3vSIC0kWqWE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F3vSIC0kWqWE&d=G5okL0FRdGxf9J%2FhKIH%2FPSwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=1e0395e6\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/3vSIC0kWqWE</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gamebase.com.tw/news/topic/98902215/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamebase.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ftopic%2F98902215%2F&d=G5okL0FRdGxf9J%2FhKIH%2FPSwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=61c03bef\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gamebase.com.tw/news/topic/98902215/</a>"},{"pid":"8065a2f8fba3f7a3221ded723845daf745cf9638","tid":443453,"uid":152533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T14:54:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d6428249d48c797ca0cde6f09e9d5280c65720c","tid":443453,"uid":17352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T02:41:07.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"a0df401eeecdf0efa073aa5efe53a6b44769605a","tid":443453,"uid":75193,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T02:44:05.000Z","msg":"就出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39aa3e3f10e8b2c4b9840c2c5a68b7c342c87e73","tid":443453,"uid":66839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T02:52:45.000Z","ms